---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About" description="Justin Helmer — Principal Engineer.">
  <div class="page-header">
    <h1 class="page-heading">About</h1>
  </div>
  <div class="about-text">
    <p>I'm a principal engineer focused on infrastructure, AI systems, and developer tooling. Most of what I build isn't visible to end users — it's the layers that make everything else possible.</p>
    <p>17 years of writing software professionally. Cal Poly SLO, then Macy's (mobile platform), Intellimize, and more recently the systems architecture side of things.</p>
    <p>I think in systems and primitives. This site is my notebook and sandbox — it evolves as I do.</p>
  </div>
</Base>

<style>
  .about-text {
    max-width: 560px;
    font-size: 16px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .about-text p + p {
    margin-top: 1.5em;
  }
</style>
